Félix Tshisekedi asololi na Uhuru Kenyatta mpe Raïla Odinga na Nairobi






Cour constitutionnelle endimaki ete Félix Tshisekedi alobaki maponami na 38,57%. Kasi Martin Fayulu aboyi mpe amisakoli mokonzi.